\f0\fs18 The Lenape listened blankly. The foremost said, "You think to fly space in a barge?"\f1\fs24\par
\f0\fs18 "In two barges, face to face, welded together."\f1\fs24\par
\f0\fs18 "Impossible."\f1\fs24\par
