\pard\fi288\sl240\slmult1\qj\f0\fs18 Barch threw down the paper. "It goes on from there. Barch this, Barch that!" He ran his hand through his hair. "What beats me is, how did it get out?"\f1\fs24\par
\pard\fi192\sl-245\slmult0\qj\f0\fs18 "Somebody must have spilled the beans," said Tim blandly.\f1\fs24\par
