\f0\fs18 Barch glared.\f1\fs24\par
\f0\fs18 "Take it easy," said Tim. "You know you love it."\f1\fs24\par
\f0\fs18 Barch laughed. "It might get me a job. I borrowed five hundred bucks from my uncle. He said it was all my own fault, that I never should have fooled around the Lekthwans to begin with."\f1\fs24\par
