\f0\fs18 She looked to where the young Acting Commissioner conferred with a tall majestic Lekthwan in a claret-red cloak. "If you cared to come to Lekthwa\emdash to study, or for curiosity\emdash  you would be the guest of myself and of my people for as long as you liked."\f1\fs24\par
