\pard\fi192\sl-245\slmult0\qj\f0\fs18 "No." Barch looked back along the avenues of the past. "I had a sneaking hunch that they might be right when they claimed to be superior, and it hurt my vanity. Now I- know better. I don't have any personal feeling either for or against Lekthwans. We're all humans.... Oh, I've changed all right."\f1\fs24\par
