\f0\fs18 Barch started to protest, then caught himself up short. Perhaps he had not changed so much in five years as he had thought. "Human minds are just too damn complex," he said inconsequentially.\f1\fs24\par
\pard\fi192\sl-245\slmult0\qj\f0\fs18 Komeitk Lelianr shrugged; she seemed to have lost interest in the conversation.\f1\fs24\par
